66.7	Elmore_Leonard	Elmore Leonard	Elmore John Leonard Jr. (born October 11, 1925), better known as Elmore Leonard, is an American novelist and screenwriter. His earliest published novels in the 1950s were westerns, but Leonard went on to specialize in crime fiction and suspense thrillers, many of which have been adapted into motion pictures.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4d/Elmore_Leonard.jpg/220px-Elmore_Leonard.jpg
